title: Flight Simulator 2020 - Addon spotlight - Pearl Harbor alive - version 1.0
description:
In this video we will look at Pearl Harbor alive which is a really nice addon which adds multiple details to Pearl Harbor including multiple navy vessels and a soccer stadium. 

If you also want to give this addon a try download your own copy from:
